      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Milwaukee road, asking for\nterminal franchise privileges from\nthe Seattle city council, has con-\nscented to all of the principal con-\ntentions of the city engineer and\ncorporations committee, agreeing\nthat sufficient overhead bridges\nshall be built in the tidelands dis\ntrict, over railroad tracks after\n1912, whenever the city so demands\nand that these bridges shall be of\napproximately the widths fixed by\nCity Engineer Thompson."
    }
